1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Thank you very much, Vincent.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:04,000
多謝,Vincent.

3
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:06,000
Good morning, everyone.

4
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:10,000
Special good morning to all the mothers here today.

5
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:13,000
一個特別的問候向所有的母親。

6
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:15,000
I wish you a happy Mother's Day.

7
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:18,000
願你有一個快樂的母親節。

8
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:20,000
It's wonderful to be with you again.

9
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:23,000
很高興能夠再一次來到你們的當中。

10
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:26,000
And I thank Pastor Har for inviting me.

11
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,000
亦都多謝夏牧師來到邀請我。

12
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:34,000
When he invited me, I did not know the day that he invited me for was Mother's Day.

13
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:39,000
當他邀請我來講道的時候,我原本不知道這一天就是母親節。

14
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:42,000
Mother's Day is a difficult day to preach.

15
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:45,000
因為母親節是很難講道的一個日子。

16
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,000
Because it's a hard day for many women.

17
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:51,000
因為對很多的婦女來說是一個心痛的日子。

18
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Many would like to be mothers and do not have children.

19
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,000
有很多人是想有小孩,但是沒有這樣的機會。

20
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:02,000
Others have had children who have passed away.

21
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:06,000
有些母親甚至有些兒子已經過世了。

22
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:12,000
Others have divisions in their families and are grieving over their separation from loved ones.

23
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,000
或者有些母親因為他們家庭的爭執的緣故,

24
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:18,000
是為了他們的家庭來傷痛。

25
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:23,000
And on Mother's Day, we often promote an idealized view of women.

26
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:28,000
很多時候我們講道的時候會常常提到一個很理想的母親是怎樣。

27
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:30,000
And that can be discouraging to women.

28
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:34,000
但是對於某些的婦女來說是一個反面的作用。

29
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:37,000
Because life is often far from perfect.

30
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:41,000
因為生命裡面是不是完美的。

31
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:48,000
This morning I do not want to present an idealized mother or a cardboard character to you.

32
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:54,000
今天我所講的信息不希望集中於一個理想的母親,

33
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:56,000
或者標榜一個母親是怎樣。

34
00:01:56,000 --> 00:02:00,000
I will try to present a realistic picture of what it means to be a mother.

35
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:05,000
我希望來形容一個母親,一個真實的母親應該是怎樣。

36
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:08,000
We are going to study a woman whose life was not easy.

37
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:14,000
我們今天所查考的是一個不容易過的母親的生活。

38
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,000
And yet she found meaning in God.

39
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:20,000
但是她在基督裡面能夠找到她的意義。

40
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:23,000
And she was used by God in her home and in her nation.

41
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:27,000
她在她的家庭,在她的國家是被神所用。

42
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:31,000
The woman we are going to look at today is Hannah in the book of 1 Samuel.

43
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:35,000
今天我們所說的婦女在撒姆爾基上。

44
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:42,000
And we are going to see Hannah's trials, her trust, and her triumph.

45
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:47,000
我們看到Hannah這個人三方面,一個是她經歷的考驗,

46
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:51,000
她對神的信靠,和她得勝的經歷。

47
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:54,000
We are going to learn from Hannah that a godly woman

48
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:59,000
is a woman who triumphs over her trials by trusting in God.

49
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:02,000
我們會學習一個敬虔的婦人,

50
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:06,000
因為她的信靠在神的使領裡面能夠得勝。

51
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:10,000
So let's look at her story in 1 Samuel chapters 1 and 2.

52
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:16,000
我們今天所看的是撒姆爾基上第一章和第二章。

53
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:20,000
Hannah lived about the same time as the events in the book of Ruth.

54
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:27,000
Hannah她本身活著的時候大概是路加那本書的時代。

55
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:30,000
That was the time of the judges,

56
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:33,000
and it was a very dark time in Israel's history.

57
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:35,000
那時候是一個事實的時代,

58
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:38,000
也是以色列一個很黑暗的時期。

59
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:41,000
We read that she lived in the city of Ramah,

60
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:44,000
about five miles north of Jerusalem.

61
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,000
剛才我們閱讀的經文裡面,

62
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:49,000
我們知道她在拉瑪所飛的地方,

63
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:53,000
是在距離耶路撒冷大概是五里之遠。

64
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:56,000
She was married to a man named Elkanah.

65
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:59,000
她嫁了給一個人叫做以尼加拿。

66
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,000
He was apparently a prosperous man.

67
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:05,000
他可能是一個比較富有的人。

68
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:10,000
Because he has two wives and he seems to have a distinguished pedigree.

69
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:13,000
因為他有兩個老婆,

70
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:20,000
而且他的家族的族譜可以見到他是一個很好的家族出來的。

71
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:23,000
His other wife's name was Penina.

72
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:26,000
他另外一個太太叫做比利娜。

73
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:30,000
It's presumed that Hannah was his first wife.

74
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:34,000
Hannah本身可能是第一個的老婆。

75
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,000
Because she is named first.

76
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:39,000
因為她的名字是列在之前。

77
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:44,000
It may be that he married Penina because Hannah was barren.

78
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:49,000
他可能和比利娜結婚是因為Hannah沒有小孩。

79
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:56,000
And having children to continue his family line and inherit his land was very important.

80
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,000
在當時來說,能夠生育兒女,

81
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:01,000
能夠承受家產是一個很重要的事情。

82
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:05,000
The passage we read this morning describes Hannah's trials.

83
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:10,000
今日我們所看到的故事是講到Hannah所經歷的考驗。

84
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:13,000
Her trials are related to her barrenness.

85
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:17,000
她的考驗就是因為她不能夠生育兒女。

86
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:24,000
Our passage emphasizes that she had no children and that the Lord had closed her womb.

87
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:31,000
在我們所讀的經文裏面,我們看到她不能夠生育,因為神令她不能夠生育。

88
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:36,000
It also says that Penina, Elkanah's other wife, had children.

89
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:40,000
他亦都提到比利娜另有一個妻子有兒女。

90
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:43,000
Penina was Hannah's rival.

91
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:47,000
比利娜和Hannah是敵對的。

92
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:52,000
She used to provoke Hannah grievously and irritate her.

93
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:57,000
因為比利娜視上用找尋的機會來帶大,來激動她。

94
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:59,000
She did this because she had no children.

95
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:02,000
因為她沒有生育到任何的兒女。

96
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:08,000
Perhaps Penina reminded Hannah of passages like Deuteronomy 7, verses 13 through 14.

97
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:15,000
很可能比利娜利用生命記第七章所提到關於神的祝福。

98
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:21,000
That passage describes the Lord's blessing on people who obey Him and keep the covenant with Him.

99
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:29,000
那段經文提到神如何將福氣賜給所有信服祂的人。

100
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:35,000
It says the Lord will love you and bless you and multiply you.

101
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:42,000
在那段經文,生命記十三章提到神必愛你,賜福於你。

102
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:48,000
He will also bless the fruit of your womb and the fruit of your ground.

103
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:59,000
第十四節提到你的男女不能生育,生畜也不能生育。

104
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:05,000
And there shall not be male or female barren among you or among your livestock.

105
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:14,000
剛才提到神會賜福你所生產的男女和生畜都能生產。

106
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:19,000
So perhaps Penina reminded Hannah of this promise of blessing.

107
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:26,000
可能比利娜利用這個來向哈拿提醒神對他們的祝福。

108
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:31,000
And it's likely she suggested that Hannah had not been obedient to God.

109
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:36,000
可能她會說,哈拿你不來信服神,所以你有這樣的情況。

110
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:39,000
And therefore Hannah had been cursed by God with barrenness.

111
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:44,000
所以神會咒詛哈拿使她不能生育。

112
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:47,000
Elkanah's family worshipped the God of Israel.

113
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:51,000
伊利加拿這個家族是敬拜神。

114
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:57,000
And they went up to the tabernacle or central sanctuary for the main Jewish festivals.

115
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:02,000
所以每次他們都會去到會幕,就是那個聖所的中心來敬拜神。

116
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:06,000
Those were Passover and Pentecost and tabernacles.

117
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:12,000
重要的節日是包括如月節、五旬節和鑄鵬節。

118
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:19,000
These were times of joy when the Israelites would celebrate God's blessings on the year's crops.

119
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:24,000
在這個節日裏面,那些以色列人會很高興來歡樂和飲宴,

120
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:28,000
因為神賜福給他們地上的土產。

121
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:33,000
But these times of celebration must have been especially hard for Hannah because she was barren.

122
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:40,000
但是在慶祝的時候可能對哈拿來說是特別困難的時期,因為她是沒有子女。

123
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:45,000
The women would bring their children and they would talk of their homes and their family lives.

124
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:53,000
可能其他的婦女會將他們的子女帶過來,在那個時候他們一起講一些家事。

125
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:57,000
And Hannah would have no children to talk about or to show to the other women.

126
00:08:57,000 --> 00:09:02,000
但是哈拿本身因為沒有子女,不能夠將她的子女帶到那些婦人當中

127
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:05,000
來跟他們分享。

128
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:09,000
At these festivals, the people would offer animal sacrifices to the Lord.

129
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:14,000
在那個節日裏面,那時候的人會將一些獻祭獻給神。

130
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:21,000
And the priest would then give them back some of the meat from the sacrifices to eat in a family meal.

131
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:24,000
但是那時候的祭司就說,當你獻上的東西,

132
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:29,000
他會將一部分所獻上的禮物歸還給奉獻的人。

133
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:35,000
And so Elkanah would then give the meat from the sacrifice to his family for them to eat.

134
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:40,000
所以以尼加拿作為一個家主,會將那些祭肉來分給他們的家人。

135
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:43,000
And he'd give a double portion to Hannah.

136
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:48,000
在這個情況底下,他將雙份來交給哈拿。

137
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:54,000
The Bible says he did this because he loved her, even though the Lord had closed her womb.

138
00:09:54,000 --> 00:10:00,000
他這樣做是因為他愛哈拿,雖然是神令他不能夠生育。

139
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:05,000
He apparently wanted to assure her of his love and commitment to her.

140
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:12,000
可能他藉著這個方法來肯定他對哈拿的愛和承諾。

141
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:14,000
Even though the Lord had closed her womb.

142
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:17,000
雖然他是沒有任何的子女。

143
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:22,000
This act of love apparently caused Penina to become jealous of Hannah.

144
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:28,000
可能在這個情況底下,更加令到比尼拿更加來嫉妒哈拿。

145
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:32,000
And it caused Penina to reproach her about her lack of children.

146
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:37,000
特別是在這個時候,特別來到辱罵她,挑動她,因為她沒有子女。

147
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:44,000
And Penina's taunting and provoking of Hannah must have become very hurtful at these times.

148
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:49,000
在這個情況底下,可能比尼拿對哈拿帶來一個極大心裏面的傷痛。

149
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:54,000
Hannah would become so troubled that she would weep and she would not be able to eat.

150
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:59,000
甚至到了一個地步,不想哭和不想吃飯。

151
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:04,000
To Alcanna's credit, he would try to comfort Hannah when she was distressed.

152
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:10,000
以利格勒其實都不錯,在這個情況底下,他常常來安慰哈拿。

153
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:12,000
He said to her, "Hannah, why do you weep?"

154
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:15,000
他會問, "哈拿,為什麼你哭啊?"

155
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:17,000
"Why don't you eat?"

156
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,000
"為什麼你不吃飯啊?"

157
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:21,000
"Why is your heart sad?"

158
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:23,000
"為什麼你的心裏面這麼傷痛呢?"

159
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:27,000
"Am I not more to you than ten sons?"

160
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:31,000
"難道我不是比十個有十個兒子更加好嗎?"

161
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:35,000
I think his questions indicate he did not really understand her.

162
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:41,000
他的問題可以表示出,他並不完全明白一個女人的心理。

163
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:46,000
And like many husbands, he far overestimated his ability to keep his wife happy.

164
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:54,000
好像很多其他的丈夫,他高估自己能夠令到他的妻子高興。

165
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:59,000
He seems to be thinking, "Dear, you have me, what more could you want?"

166
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:03,000
親愛的,如果你有我之後,你還需要些什麼呢?

167
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:07,000
My wife often reminds me that I cannot make her happy.

168
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:14,000
我的太太也經常提醒我,我不能夠完全滿足她,讓她有快樂。

169
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:17,000
The Lord is the only one who can do that.

170
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:20,000
只有神才能夠滿足她。

171
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:23,000
Alcanna did not seem to realize this.

172
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:27,000
但是伊利加拿定不了解這件事情。

173
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:30,000
So Hannah has no other person who understands her.

174
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:33,000
所以Hannah是沒有一個人能夠了解她。

175
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:37,000
She has no friends she can go to for help, and she is all alone.

176
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:42,000
她沒有一個朋友她可以去訴苦,她是自己一個很孤單的個人。

177
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:48,000
Furthermore, she knows God is the Lord of hosts, as He is described in verse 3.

178
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:54,000
在第三節的時候,她提醒我,她明白神是一個萬君之神。

179
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:58,000
This name refers to His great authority and power.

180
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:02,000
萬君之又說代表的是一個權威和能力。

181
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:06,000
And it means He is sovereign over all the hosts of heaven.

182
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:09,000
祂有管理萬物,祂的主權。

183
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:12,000
But He is the one who has shut her womb.

184
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:15,000
但是祂也是那個令她不生育的神。

185
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:18,000
And she is seemingly cursed by Him.

186
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:22,000
似乎神是在這件事情上來救助她。

187
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:25,000
However, because she knows the Lord is sovereign,

188
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:28,000
her trials are going to drive her to Him.

189
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:31,000
但是因為她知道神是一個至高神,

190
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:35,000
她所經歷的只能夠推動祂來接近神。

191
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:39,000
She realizes the Lord is the only one who can help her.

192
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:43,000
她知道神是唯一能夠幫助她的神。

193
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:45,000
And in the midst of her trials,

194
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:48,000
she demonstrates tremendous trust in the Lord.

195
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:50,000
在哈娜所經歷的考驗中,

196
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:54,000
她能夠表達對神的極大的信心。

197
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:59,000
We see her trust in chapter 1, verses 9 through 28.

198
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:07,000
在聖母耳機上第一章9-28那裡,我們看見哈娜對神的信心。

199
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:11,000
And I'm going to try to summarize that part of the story for you.

200
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:17,000
雖然我剛才沒有讀,我們就盡量簡略地跟大家講一下。

201
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,000
As far as we know,

202
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:22,000
Hannah doesn't say anything to her rival, Penina.

203
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:29,000
據我們所知,哈娜並沒有跟比利娜講任何不好的說話。

204
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:33,000
She realizes there's a greater adversary than Penina.

205
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:37,000
因為她相信有一個攻擊她的極大的攻擊者。

206
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:41,000
In all of her trouble and testing, she controls her tongue.

207
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:44,000
在整個過程,在困難和考驗中,

208
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:48,000
她控制她的舌頭不說不應該的說話。

209
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,000
And she goes straight to God.

210
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,000
她直接來到神的面前。

211
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,000
The Bible says,

212
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:56,000
after they had eaten and drunk in Shiloh,

213
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:59,000
Hannah rose and went into the tabernacle.

214
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,000
在聖經這裡講到,

215
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:03,000
當他們吃完之後,喝完之後,

216
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:06,000
在侍羅那裡飲喝之後,

217
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:09,000
哈娜來到神的會幕之前,

218
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:12,000
Now Eli the priest was sitting on the seat

219
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:15,000
beside the doorpost of the temple of the Lord.

220
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:23,000
當時祭司以利坐在會幕前的柱子旁邊。

221
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:26,000
She was deeply distressed and prayed to the Lord

222
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:28,000
and wept bitterly.

223
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:31,000
當時哈娜非常痛苦,

224
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:33,000
在神的面前哭泣。

225
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:35,000
And she vowed a vow.

226
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:37,000
她對神做一個承諾。

227
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,000
And she said,

228
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,000
Oh Lord of hosts,

229
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:42,000
if you will indeed look on the affliction of your servant

230
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:44,000
and remember me.

231
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:46,000
在首次她就講到,

232
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:47,000
許個願,

233
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:49,000
耶和華,萬君之耶和華,

234
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:52,000
如果你垂聽僕女的苦情,

235
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:54,000
顧念不忘父女,

236
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,000
賜我一個兒子,

237
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:58,000
我就使他終生歸於耶和華。

238
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,000
And if you won't forget your servant,

239
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:02,000
but give me a son,

240
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:04,000
如果你能夠賜我一個兒子,

241
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:06,000
then I will give him to the Lord

242
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:08,000
all the days of his life,

243
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:10,000
我將他一生歸給你,

244
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:12,000
and no razor shall touch his head.

245
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:16,000
她不會用剃刀來剃他的頭。

246
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,000
These verses show us

247
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:19,000
that one day it was all too much

248
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:21,000
for Hannah to bear.

249
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,000
這裡我們看見,

250
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:24,000
在這一天裡面,

251
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:26,000
所有的事情對於哈娜來說

252
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:28,000
是實在忍受不住的。

253
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,000
And greatly grieved in heart,

254
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,000
she goes to the tabernacle

255
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:33,000
to pray to the Lord of hosts.

256
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:36,000
在一個極度傷痛的當中,

257
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:38,000
她來到神的面前來禱告。

258
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,000
She feels forgotten by God.

259
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:42,000
她覺得神是忘記了她了。

260
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:44,000
And she asks the Lord to remember her.

261
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:46,000
她求神來紀念她。

262
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:47,000
She promises the Lord

263
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:49,000
that if he will give her a son,

264
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:51,000
then she will give him to the Lord

265
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:53,000
all the days of his life.

266
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:55,000
如果神賜她一個兒子的話,

267
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,000
她願意將這個兒子歸給神,

268
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:59,000
一生來侍奉神。

269
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:01,000
She also promises that her son

270
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:04,000
will be a Nazarite for his life.

271
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,000
她答應神,

272
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:08,000
她的兒子要成為一個拿西爾人。

273
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:10,000
There are only three people in the Bible

274
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:13,000
who had a lifetime commitment to be a Nazarite.

275
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:15,000
在聖經裡面只有三個人物

276
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:17,000
是作為一個拿西爾人。

277
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:21,000
They are Samson, Samuel and John the Baptist.

278
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:27,000
他是參孫薩姆爾和施洗約翰。

279
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:29,000
This means he will eat nothing

280
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:31,000
produced by the grapevine.

281
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:33,000
作為一個拿西爾人的意義

282
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:36,000
就是他不會吃葡萄樹上所長的東西。

283
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:38,000
That means he will abstain

284
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:40,000
from the normal enjoyments of life

285
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:42,000
so he can serve the Lord.

286
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,000
意思就是說,

287
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:46,000
他會脫離一切一般人的享用

288
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:48,000
專心來侍奉神。

289
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:50,000
He will not go near a dead body.

290
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:54,000
他不會接近任何死的事物。

291
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:56,000
That means holier duties

292
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:59,000
will take precedence over the cares of this life.

293
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:01,000
意思就是說,

294
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:03,000
所有聖潔的侍奉

295
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:07,000
是比人裡面所有的經歷更加重要。

296
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:09,000
And also he will not cut his hair.

297
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:11,000
而且他不會剃頭。

298
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:13,000
Meaning he will be different from the world

299
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:15,000
and even from ordinary believers.

300
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,000
意思就是說,

301
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:20,000
他不會和一般人一樣。

302
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:22,000
This is a major commitment.

303
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:25,000
這是一個極端重要的遺身。

304
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:27,000
So then overcome with grief,

305
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:31,000
she continues to pray intensely before the Lord.

306
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:33,000
哈拿在極度憂傷的裡面

307
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:36,000
不斷地向神傾心吐怡。

308
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:38,000
And when Eli the priest sees her,

309
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:41,000
he thinks she is drunk and he reprimands her.

310
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:43,000
當以利見到這個婦人的時候,

311
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:45,000
他以為她是喝醉了酒,

312
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,000
而且來斥責她。

313
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,000
But she explains to him

314
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:50,000
that she is not drunk.

315
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:52,000
哈拿就向以利解釋說,

316
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,000
我不是喝醉。

317
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:55,000
She is deeply troubled,

318
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:57,000
pouring out her soul to the Lord.

319
00:18:57,000 --> 00:19:03,000
極致地仇苦,來將自己向神傾心吐怡。

320
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:06,000
So Eli the priest then blesses her

321
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,000
and prays for her.

322
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:10,000
以利就在這個時候來祝福她,

323
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:11,000
為她來祈禱。

324
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:13,000
Then she leaves her burden there.

325
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:15,000
她就將她的重擔

326
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:17,000
在那個時候完全放下。

327
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:20,000
And she goes back to the meal with her family.

328
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:24,000
回去和他們家人一起享用那種飲宴。

329
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:28,000
The Bible says that her face was no longer downcast.

330
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:30,000
而且聖經裡面講到,

331
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:34,000
她念想已經不再帶任何的仇慾。

332
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:37,000
She had done more than release her psychological burden.

333
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:39,000
所以我們看見她不單止是放下

334
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:41,000
她心裡面那種的重擔。

335
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:43,000
She had prayed to the Lord

336
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:44,000
that He would remember her.

337
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:46,000
她是向神來祈禱,

338
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:48,000
神來紀念她。

339
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:50,000
And she had promised to honor God

340
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:53,000
with the blessing that He would give her.

341
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:56,000
所以她向神許了願,

342
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:59,000
求神來將她的福氣賜給她。

343
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:01,000
Also God's representative,

344
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:04,000
the priest, had blessed her and prayed for her.

345
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:07,000
而且代表神的祭司已經祝福她,

346
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:09,000
為她來禱告。

347
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:11,000
So the next morning,

348
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:13,000
Alcanna and his family

349
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:15,000
worship again in the tabernacle.

350
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:16,000
第二天,

351
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:20,000
伊利卡那在會幕那裡來敬拜神。

352
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:22,000
And then they return home.

353
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:24,000
完了之後,他們就回家了。

354
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:26,000
And after they return home,

355
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,000
God remembers Hannah.

356
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:29,000
當他們回到家的時候,

357
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:31,000
神紀念Hannah.

358
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,000
And she conceives,

359
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:34,000
and she bears a son.

360
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:35,000
神紀念她,

361
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,000
讓她能夠懷孕,

362
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:38,000
生了一個兒子。

363
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,000
She names him Samuel,

364
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:42,000
which means "Heard of the Lord".

365
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:44,000
薩姆爾這個名字,

366
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:46,000
就是說神已經聽了禱告。

367
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:48,000
Because she had asked the Lord for him,

368
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:50,000
and the Lord did not forget her.

369
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:52,000
因為Hannah向神祈求,

370
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:55,000
神並沒有忘記她。

371
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:57,000
One evidence of Hannah's trust

372
00:20:57,000 --> 00:20:59,000
is her focus on the Lord.

373
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:01,000
其中一個證明Hannah的信心

374
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:03,000
就是因為她將她的注意力

375
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:05,000
集中在耶和華身上。

376
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:07,000
Three times in this passage,

377
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:09,000
it says Hannah was before the Lord.

378
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:10,000
在這段經文,

379
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,000
她三次提到說,

380
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:14,000
她在神的面前。

381
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,000
In 112,

382
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:18,000
she continued praying before the Lord.

383
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,000
在第一章第十二節那裡,

384
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:23,000
她不斷地在神的面前祈禱。

385
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,000
In 115,

386
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:27,000
she tells Eli the priest she was not drunk.

387
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:30,000
在第一章第十五節那裡,

388
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:32,000
她提到和以利說,

389
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:34,000
她不是喝醉酒,

390
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:38,000
而是將她在神的面前傾心圖義。

391
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:41,000
She is pouring out her soul before the Lord.

392
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:43,000
她將她所有的心思

393
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:45,000
向神傾倒出來。

394
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:46,000
In 119,

395
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:49,000
she and her family worship before the Lord.

396
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:50,000
在第一章第十九節那裡,

397
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:53,000
她在神的面前來敬拜。

398
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:54,000
For Hannah,

399
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:58,000
the Lord was the most real thing in her life.

400
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:59,000
對於Hannah來說,

401
00:21:59,000 --> 00:22:04,000
神是最真實的一件事情。

402
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:05,000
There were probably other people

403
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:08,000
in the tabernacle when she prayed.

404
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,000
可能當她祈禱的時候,

405
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:12,000
有其他人同時在會幕那裡。

406
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:14,000
We know Eli the priest was there.

407
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:16,000
所以我們也知道

408
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:18,000
以利當時也在那裡。

409
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:20,000
But Hannah was only conscious

410
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:21,000
of the Lord's presence.

411
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:23,000
但是在眾人當中,

412
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:27,000
Hannah只能夠感覺神自己的同在。

413
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:30,000
The Lord was bigger and more real to her

414
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:32,000
than anything else in life.

415
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:36,000
神比任何事情更大和更重要。

416
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:39,000
She lived with the consciousness of God.

417
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:42,000
她活在神的意識當中。

418
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:45,000
And that is evidence of her focus on the Lord

419
00:22:45,000 --> 00:22:47,000
and her trust in Him.

420
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:48,000
所以從此我們看到

421
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:52,000
Hannah的注意力就在神的身上。

422
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:54,000
Another evidence of her trust in the Lord

423
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:57,000
is how she keeps the vow that she made to the Lord.

424
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:59,000
另外一樣我們看到她的信心

425
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:04,000
就是她怎樣來還她的緣。

426
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:05,000
After Samuel was born,

427
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:07,000
it would have been easy for Hannah

428
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:09,000
to forget to keep her vow.

429
00:23:09,000 --> 00:23:11,000
當她兒子撒姆爾出世的時候,

430
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:12,000
她很容易說

431
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:15,000
我忘記我自己對神的承諾。

432
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:17,000
She surely loved Samuel

433
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:19,000
and wanted to keep him for herself.

434
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:21,000
當然她會很愛這個撒姆爾,

435
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:24,000
想完全地擁有這個兒子。

436
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:26,000
But from the time of his birth,

437
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:28,000
she begins to prepare him

438
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:29,000
to fulfill this vow.

439
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:33,000
但是我們看到她從這個兒子出生,

440
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:36,000
她就開始準備怎樣來還這個緣。

441
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:38,000
She had made this vow to God.

442
00:23:38,000 --> 00:23:41,000
她向神立下這個緣,

443
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:45,000
And now it must be fulfilled by Samuel.

444
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:46,000
但是她所立的緣

445
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:51,000
是需要她的兒子很自願地來還這個緣。

446
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:52,000
Elkanah, her husband,

447
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:54,000
will also have to cooperate

448
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:57,000
if she is going to be able to fulfill this vow.

449
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:59,000
她也需要伊麗嘉娜她的丈夫

450
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:01,000
來同意她還這個緣。

451
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:04,000
Because the child belongs to him too.

452
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:05,000
因為這個兒子

453
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:08,000
也同時是她的兒子。

454
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:09,000
So Hannah had to produce

455
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:12,000
or develop a spirit in Samuel.

456
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:13,000
所以我們看到Hannah

457
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:16,000
是需要在這個撒姆爾上

458
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:19,000
養成一種特別的自願性格。

459
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:20,000
So that he would be willing

460
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:23,000
to let her leave him at the tabernacle

461
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:24,000
to serve the Lord.

462
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:26,000
到有一天她能夠自願地

463
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:28,000
讓媽媽離開他

464
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:31,000
而自己留在這個會幕來侍奉神。

465
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:33,000
She has three years to do this

466
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:35,000
before he will be weaned.

467
00:24:35,000 --> 00:24:37,000
所以有三年的時間

468
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:39,000
她才能夠斷奶。

469
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:40,000
For this reason

470
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:42,000
she doesn't go up to the feast

471
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:43,000
at the tabernacle

472
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,000
for the next three years.

473
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:46,000
所以因為這個原因

474
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:49,000
Hannah沒有跟著她的家族和丈夫

475
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:50,000
上去敬拜神。

476
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:53,000
Instead, she stays home with Samuel.

477
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:56,000
反而她留下來與撒姆爾一起。

478
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:58,000
And she spends every minute she has

479
00:24:58,000 --> 00:25:01,000
in preparing him to leave her.

480
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:03,000
所以她用這個時候

481
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:04,000
每分每秒的時候

482
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:06,000
來準備他

483
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:09,000
這個兒子離開自己。

484
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:12,000
So Samuel is weaned at the age of three.

485
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:15,000
撒姆爾大概是三歲的時候就斷奶了。

486
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:17,000
And Hannah takes him to the tabernacle

487
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:19,000
and gives him into the hands

488
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:21,000
of Eli the priest.

489
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:22,000
所以斷奶之後

490
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:24,000
她帶著這個兒子

491
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:25,000
去到以利的面前

492
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:27,000
來將他獻給神。

493
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,000
She reminds Eli

494
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,000
that she is the woman

495
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:31,000
who is praying for a child

496
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:33,000
there in the tabernacle.

497
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:35,000
她會向這個以利提到

498
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:37,000
她就是那個婦人

499
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:40,000
在這個會幕裏面求一個兒子。

500
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:42,000
And God has answered her prayer.

501
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:44,000
神已經答應這個祈求。

502
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:51,000
Sorry, I lost my place for just a moment.

503
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:53,000
OK, here we go.

504
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:56,000
Since God gave Samuel to her,

505
00:25:56,000 --> 00:25:59,000
she is now going to give him back to the Lord.

506
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:01,000
因為神將這個兒子給了她

507
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:04,000
她願意將這個兒子歸還給神。

508
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:05,000
And he will serve the Lord

509
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:07,000
as long as he lives.

510
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:11,000
她願意這個兒子一生來侍奉神。

511
00:26:11,000 --> 00:26:12,000
She does this

512
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:14,000
knowing that now she will only be able

513
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:17,000
to see her son about one time a year.

514
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:19,000
她知道以後

515
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:21,000
她只能夠一年見她的兒子一次。

516
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:22,000
And that will be

517
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:24,000
when she comes to the tabernacle for the feast.

518
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:26,000
就是當她的家族去到會幕

519
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:28,000
來敬拜憲制義的時候。

520
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:36,000
從第二章裏面我們看到

521
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:39,000
會幕其實是一個很危險的地方。

522
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:45,000
其實是一個很危險

523
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:47,000
讓她將這個小孩留下。

524
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:53,000
因為以利的兒子是非常邪惡。

525
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:57,000
而且以利本身也不能夠

526
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:59,000
控制這兩個的兒子。

527
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:05,000
他們甚至是與一些婦人

528
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:08,000
在會幕事後的婦人來糾合。

529
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:17,000
她從這個被人帶上去聖殿

530
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:19,000
去到會幕憲制的祭物裏面

531
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:21,000
將那個來搶奪。

532
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:26,000
對於這個撒慕爾來說

533
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:28,000
那裏沒有一個基督教的學校。

534
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:34,000
那裏沒有一些青少年的士工

535
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:36,000
能夠栽培他。

536
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:46,000
哈娜是將這個所愛的兒子

537
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:48,000
所渴求的兒子

538
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:50,000
將他放在一個這樣的情況下。

539
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:54,000
這個不是一個很理想的情況。

540
00:27:54,000 --> 00:28:01,000
可能哈娜就會很有藉口

541
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:04,000
來說我不願意將兒子

542
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:06,000
放在這樣的地方。

543
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:12,000
但是我們看到哈娜是

544
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:15,000
將她的注意力是集中在耶和華身上

545
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:17,000
而不是看到她周圍的環境。

546
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:21,000
她所做的是誰所答應神的。

547
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:25,000
她對神有一個很大的信心。

548
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:34,000
其實我們都應該將我們的兒女

549
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:36,000
獻給神。

550
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:39,000
因為他們是神給我們的禮物。

551
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:44,000
我不能夠完全地擁有我們的兒女。

552
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:48,000
我們是愚笨的

553
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:50,000
如果我們想完全地擁有他們。

554
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:56,000
但是如果我們做一個聰明的人的時候

555
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:59,000
我們會盡量在我們的兒女面前

556
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:01,000
來表示我們對神的信心。

557
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:03,000
希望他們以後會服侍神。

558
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:11,000
我們知道哈娜會做到這個。

559
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,000
因為我們看到

560
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:16,000
撒姆爾能夠專心來侍奉耶和華。

561
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:24,000
在聖經裡面講到

562
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:28,000
撒姆爾在神的面前侍奉耶和華。

563
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:33,000
他在神的面前來侍納。

564
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:40,000
他的注意力就在神耶和華的身上

565
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:42,000
就好像他母親一樣。

566
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:50,000
我們看到哈娜本身的考驗

567
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:52,000
和她對神的信心。

568
00:29:52,000 --> 00:29:58,000
現在我們來看看哈娜本身的特性。

569
00:29:58,000 --> 00:30:09,000
在第二章裡面提到哈娜的禱告

570
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:12,000
她說除了神之外沒有其他的。

571
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:17,000
她知道她的丈夫不能夠帶給她快樂。

572
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:24,000
她更加有智慧地知道

573
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:28,000
她的兒女不能夠帶給她完全的喜樂。

574
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:36,000
只有一位能夠完完全全帶給她完全的快樂。

575
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:39,000
就是主耶穌基督。

576
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:47,000
她知道只有神能夠滿足她的心。

577
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:53,000
在第二章裡面她這樣說:

578
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:59,000
她說:我的心因耶和華高舉

579
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:05,000
我的口向受敵來張開。

580
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:09,000
對不起,我漏了句。

581
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:12,000
我的口向受敵來張開。

582
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:19,000
因為我因為耶和華的救恩而歡樂。

583
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:23,000
只有耶和華為聖。

584
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:30,000
因為除他以外並有可比的。

585
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:37,000
也都是沒有一個盤石像我們的神。

586
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:47,000
哈娜勝過她的願望和她的懷疑。

587
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:53,000
她能夠勝過她的自憐。

588
00:31:53,000 --> 00:32:01,000
她勝過她的自我中心和依靠自己。

589
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:11,000
她勝過所有沒有意義的事物,高傲和所有的惡勢力。

590
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:17,000
她能夠得勝因為她依靠耶和華。

591
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:25,000
她在極大的壓力之下能夠保持她的尊嚴和自制。

592
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:35,000
她並沒有因為傷害她的人而以牙還牙。

593
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:43,000
她的注意力就是集中在神給她要做的事。

594
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:57,000
她將所有的精力放在撒慕爾的身上,來準備她做侍奉耶和華的工作。

595
00:32:57,000 --> 00:33:07,000
哈娜相信神完全是管理她的生命。

596
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:14,000
不單止是她所遇到的試煉和所有的考驗。

597
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:21,000
她知道一件事就是,她所遇到的事並不是一個錯誤。

598
00:33:21,000 --> 00:33:27,000
所有發生在她身上的事,神都有一個目的在此。

599
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:34,000
可能所發生的事不是她願意所選擇的。

600
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:53,000
她相信她所經歷的所有情況是為了彰顯神的榮耀和他的國度,而且是為了讓她得到益處。

601
00:33:53,000 --> 00:34:03,000
撒姆爾後來成為以色列一個很重要的屬靈領袖。

602
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:14,000
他是高納以色列頭兩個王,就是索羅和大衛。

603
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:25,000
他幫助以色列人脫離菲律斯人的壓迫。

604
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:33,000
他復甦了以色列的屬靈的光景。

605
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:41,000
但是神也是很豐足地祝福哈娜。

606
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:49,000
她是一個很敬虔的母親的模範。

607
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:54,000
她不是擁有所有的東西。

608
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:59,000
她有很多的考驗和失望。

609
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:06,000
但是在哈娜的生活上,我們能夠學到一個很重要的功課。

610
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:14,000
就是一個很敬虔的婦人會將她的心專注在耶和華,將所有的榮耀帶給她的神。

611
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:30,000
神是她生命中最重要的人物。

612
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:42,000
她的立志是要將她所學到的專注傳給她的兒女和周圍的人。

613
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:46,000
讓我們一起來祈禱。

614
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:54,000
天上的父神,我們感謝祢,因為祢是萬君的耶和華。

615
00:35:54,000 --> 00:36:02,000
祢是完全掌管我們生命中任何的情況。

616
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:09,000
我祈求祢幫助我們怎樣在祢面前活著。

617
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:18,000
讓我們能夠不斷地在每一時每一刻體驗祢的同在和祢的愛。

618
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:28,000
當我們在試驗和危難當中的時候,讓我們專心地仰望祢。

619
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:35,000
幫助我們不去擔心其他人怎樣去想。

620
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:40,000
讓我們繼續能夠專心地忠於祢。

621
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:45,000
我們感謝祢給我們的母親。

622
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:51,000
我們感謝這裡會中所有的母親。

623
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:59,000
我們感謝他們在我們的家庭裡面,在我們的家庭裡面所付出的代價。

624
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:06,000
我們懇求祢將祢豐滿的恩典來賜給他們。

625
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:10,000
同主耶穌名給,阿們。

